OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCouncil financial crisis   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'out of control', MPs warn 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The financial crisis facing England's  
OL,6, councils is "out of control" with even 
OL,7, well-run local authorities at risk of  
OL,8, going bust, MPs have warned.           
OL,10,FA cross-party committee said the       
OL,11,Fgovernment must plug a #4bn funding gap
OL,12,Fto avoid a "severe impact" on services.
OL,14,FThey also called for council tax to be 
OL,15,Freformed, describing the current system
OL,16,Fas "outdated" and "regressive".        
OL,18,FThe government said it recognised the  
OL,19,Fchallenges facing councils and had     
OL,20,Fannounced an extra #600m in support.   
